<p><b>A WEEKLY TIP ON CARING FOR OUR COMMON HOME</b>.
“There is a nobility in the duty to care for creation
through little daily actions, and it is wonderful how
education can bring about real changes in lifestyle.
Education in environmental responsibility can
encourage ways of acting which directly and
significantly affect the world around us...” (Pope
Francis, <i>Laudato Si</i>’, 211)</p>
