<p><b>A WELCOME AND A FAREWELL AT THE SOLANUS
CASEY CENTER</b>. The Solanus Casey Center, a program
of Catholic Community Services supported by St.
James Cathedral, has hired Corin Brown as Program
Manager. Corin shares years of experience working
with CCS at Noel House, which serves women
experiencing homelessness. We welcome her and look
